  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "We focus exclusively on long-form questions for RL training.",
    "Following the same LMbased filtering procedure used in long-form SFT data curation, we collect approximately 5K new prompts from SearchArena (Miroyan et al., 2025) and OpenScholar (Asai et al., 2024).",
    "Additionally, we sample 4K prompts from RaR (Gunjal et al., 2025) to enhance further data diversity.",
    "1 We note that, although we attempted to collect prompts from diverse sources, the questions we gathered are often still out-of-distribution (OOD) relative to those in downstream benchmarks.",
    "RL training."
  ],
